Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们这样做。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的第一个网页
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚刚在 VS Code 中手动创建的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你问我，那真的很神奇，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你，干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在您的第一个网页上。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们把它推到一边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点，然后 VS Code 到另一边。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从现在开始，我们将永远拥有，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的代码在左边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在右侧的浏览器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就可以看到我们的变化。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给我们更多的空间，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以再次，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单击此处的此选项卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侧边栏并给我们更多空间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们的实际代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你在这里看到，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有这个大而粗体的hello world。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这对应于这个 H1 元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在下面我们有这一段，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入这个视觉元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有实际的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此选项卡的标题中的页面。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以“我的第一个网页”就是我们这里的内容，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我们在这里输入的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入标题元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里写的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的 HTML 文档中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在反映在现实世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个真正的网络浏览器中。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到网络浏览器，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在使用谷歌浏览器进行测试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要写的所有代码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整个课程中。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我真的建议你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也使用谷歌浏览器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终测试您正在编写的代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这将再次，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保您有准确的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与您看到的结果相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在课程视频中。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实际上就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于第一个编码视频。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你真的会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向你展示的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本次讲座中。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上从创造开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个项目文件夹，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在 VS Code 中打开该项目文件夹。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的这个文件夹是test文件夹，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在里面，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创建一个 HTML 文件，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后添加一些代码文件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后打开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实浏览器中的 HTML 文档，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如谷歌浏览器，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们看到这个结果。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上我们代码的翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到视觉效果。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望你玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在下一个视频中见到你。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's now write our very first line of code
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and build our very first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and very small webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here we are back in VS Code,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and let's now close all of this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then we're going here to this first tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this Explorer tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in VS Code,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we always need to be inside of some folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that folder is called the project folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, right now we don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,any folders started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's actually start by doing that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I will create a folder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,right here on my desktop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically I will do all the,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all the coding will always happen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here on my desktop,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but of course you can also do it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in any other place on your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one doesn't really matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for me, it's just easier
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to have it on the desktop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm calling this folder here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,01 and Test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go back here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now click on open folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so going to my desktop,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will now select this folder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that I just created.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so this 01 Test is now our project folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we get a new welcome screen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and here we can click on new file
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to add our very first file to the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or we could also do this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by hovering here over this left sidebar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and clicking here on the new file icon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So these are two different ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of creating new files in the project folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I actually prefer this one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we are about to create
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,our very first webpage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and a webpage is basically just an HTML file,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and let's call it index.html.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's basically just the file
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with the HTML file extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we are calling it index
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because that is the default name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of the first page of any website.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So index is basically always
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the entry point to any website.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so all web projects
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,always need to have an index.html.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. So keep that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,always call your very first page index.html.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now my goal in this lecture is not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to really teach you HTML.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all I want to do is to create this file
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and to add a little bit of code to it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then see the results in the browser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you get to write
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your first line of code
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and are able to see the results
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of writing that code in a real web browser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again, I'm not really starting to teach HTML
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so instead of writing a whole page structure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as we usually need to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are going to use a small cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that we can use in VS Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So to do that, just write an exclamation mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then you can hit tab on your keyboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or you can also just click here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we get this very basic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and almost empty HTML structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it has a head and it has a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we will learn all about that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a little bit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, all I'm interested here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is for now this title of the webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's change the content here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of this title to, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"My first webpage."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course you can also write
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,something else here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then let's go inside of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is actually the part
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that we will be able to see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the browser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here, just write this less than sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then H1, which stands for heading one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then the greater than symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just like this one here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you see that then VS Code
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,actually automatically placed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this other part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So closing the H1 basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't really matter for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just write some text content in here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm writing, "Hello, world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which has kind of a standard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you write your very first line of code
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in any programming language.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So hello world is really
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a long standing tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next let's try another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again, this less than symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's try P which stands for paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VS Code automatically closes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the paragraph for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's say, "My name is Jonas."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you will of course use your own name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"And this is my very first
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,webpage."
